Step 4: 
Interfacing MQ-2 Gas Sensor (Air Quality Monitoring)


{
The MQ-2 sensor detects various gases like LPG, smoke, alcohol, propane, methane, and carbon monoxide. 
It helps monitor air pollution and gas leaks in the environment.
}


..Hardware Required:
> MQ-2 Gas Sensor Module
> Arduino uno
> Jumper Wires



>>>>Connections:
The MQ-2 sensor has both analog (A0) and digital (D0) outputs.

>MQ-2 Pin	Arduino Pin
>VCC	5V
>GND	GND
>A0	A1 (or any analog pin)


